#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Introduzione"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmix; supports several platforms and sound drivers."
msgstr "&kmix; supporta diverse piattaforme e driver sonori."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have both ALSA and Open Sound System drivers installed, &kmix; will "
"use the ALSA driver."
msgstr ""
"Se hai installato sia il driver ALSA che quello per OSS, &kmix; userà quello "
"per ALSA."

